  • Field Details

    • seatIndex

      private String seatIndex
      Ticket's seatIndex. Row represented by numbers e.g 4 for 4th row from the front, Columns represented by uppercase letters e.g B for 2nd row from the left, e.g seatIndex = "3C" -> row 3 col 3
